@Senjai: I think you are someone who wants to learn about this game...I think you should get an avatar.<br>
<br>
Reading...Thanks everybody for writing so much. I love reading...

Pointing out/explaining your Swiss cheese posting =/= arguing someone else's case for them.<br>
<br>
Also, where exactly is everyone? Only we 3 have posted within the past 24 hours. &gt;_&gt;

@jackal<br>
<br>
Why are you changing your vote in nearly every post you make?

@Senjai, you really do need to be a bit more polite, you are coming off as rude, its ok to be aggressive but not in the way you are doing it.<br>
<br>
@drmyshotgun I know that you think senjai is being a dick, but responding to him like that isn't making the situation better. Be the bigger man and ignore him or pm the mod if you think he isn't playing right. Ragequitting isn't the solution.<br>
<br>
@Jackal, if you have a problem with a player, at least try and take it up with a mod before you ragequit, you aren't helping anybody by doing that.<br>
<br>
@prolapsed brain, are you around? I would appreciate if you could answer my questions I posted to you a little ways back, I think it will help clear some things up.

@ICEninja, thanks for joining the game, the slot you replaced into was rather scummy, but it's early in the game so that can change.<br>
<br>
@Prolapsed brain, I make a decent case against you and the only response you can muster is "Oh, your just bizarre now." <br>
<br>
Normally when someone says a case of mine is bizarre I would ask them why, but at this point I don't think I'm going to get that out of you. But I'll ask anyways, How is my case bizarre?<br>
<br>
@pieceofpecanpie I agree that jackals play was also bad, but even then, he was at least giving basic reasons for his votes and suspicious. PB has not even done that. Since it is looking like jackal replaced then I'm going to wait until then till passing any judgement on him. I would consider PB more scummy than Jackal at this point.

@Majiffy, I don't intend to. I would find more lurking by PB as the perfect reason to lynch him.<br>
<br>
@PB just to be clear, if you don't give me a good reason to not vote you by the end of today, my vote is going back on.

@PC just to be clear, is your town read on PB is solely based on you seeing gooner as scum?<br>
<br>
Also, yes not commenting on something doesn't doesn't mean you are tied to that person. But when everyone else in the game has a least mentioned the person who has acquired the biggest wagon so far and you hadn't up to that point then yes it does stand out.

I do not like Senjai's attempt at hammer.<br>
<br>
@Senjai: So, you admit that you attempted to hammer without a claim from PB?

@Majffy I know he has been on your list. <br>
<br>
But you said you had made a case explaining why he was scum. You didn't. Which is why I still say you lied.

Some questions for some people.<br>
<br>
@Hiraki-your last post in day 1 suggests you want to go after senjai. Why nothing about him to start day 2?<br>
<br>
@PC,Equinox, &amp; FG, you guys should show up and post.<br>
<br>
@majiffy, since you seem to think gooner it scum, could you make<div style="display:inline;font-style:italic"> your own case </div>explaining why?<br>
<br>
@ICE, you should explain your jumping on sora, at the end of day two you are suggesting that a town flip by PB would make you suspicious of PC/Gooner.<br>
<br>
@Pecan, why is your vote suddenly on sora?

@Scott<br>
<br>
you have played with ICE before, in your playing with him did he, or didn't he give out townreads?

@everyone<br>
<br>
if someone is roleblocked, do they go somewhere or do they stay still?

@ICE, obviously I'm speaking from my PoV.<br>
<br>
Yes, from your point of view your only options seem to  be myself, hiraki, and majiffy.

@majiffy<br>
<br>
